    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Synopsis</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step back into a world of tactical battles and dreamlike adventures in <strong>Eternal Dreamers Rising</strong>: a fast-paced, battle-focused RPG where every choice of class and strategy shapes your fate. Rebuilt with new systems, graphics, and soundtrack, <i>Rising</i> brings fresh life to the series with deeper combat than ever before and all-new heroes to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💎 <strong>Loot Without Limits</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt for rare weapons, armor, and special items across endless challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292810/extras/abdaab09be250259fdbafd5e2ae398f1.poster.avif?t=1768688458\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292810/extras/abdaab09be250259fdbafd5e2ae398f1.webm?t=1768688458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292810/extras/abdaab09be250259fdbafd5e2ae398f1.mp4?t=1768688458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚔️ 14 Playable Classes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match to form over 1000 unique party combinations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292810/extras/aa304652e16dcb39f5d9e6f549850365.poster.avif?t=1768688458\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292810/extras/aa304652e16dcb39f5d9e6f549850365.webm?t=1768688458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292810/extras/aa304652e16dcb39f5d9e6f549850365.mp4?t=1768688458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎲 <strong>Mini-Games &amp; Diversions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax with dozens of fun, offbeat side activities between battles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292810/extras/20d71144058ab53443155e34a856f7cf.poster.avif?t=1768688458\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292810/extras/20d71144058ab53443155e34a856f7cf.webm?t=1768688458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292810/extras/20d71144058ab53443155e34a856f7cf.mp4?t=1768688458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What's new in Rising?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>3 New Classes</strong> — Shana, the wild gunslinger, Raze, the draconic brawler, and Corrin, the traveler!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>New Quest Type: SUPPRESSION</strong> — Face Death’s legions in brutal, large-scale encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>New Quest Type: THE SINGULARITY </strong>— Face the most powerful bosses yet in raid-like encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Expanded Loot Pool</strong> — Hundreds of new items and equipment to collect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Full Rebalance</strong> — Reworked combat, AI, and progression systems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Visual &amp; Audio Overhaul</strong> — New graphics, UI, and soundtrack for a richer experience.</p>",
